James B. BULL, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-0311
CASE NO.: 2D17-2459 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. April 27, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Case number 2D17-2459 has been classified as a nonsummary postconviction appeal. Case number 2D18-311 is a related appeal of the circuit court order denying the appointment of appellate counsel for 2D17-2459.

Appellant's notice of appeal which initiated 2D18-311 and appellant's initial brief docketed in 2D18-311 on February 26, 2018, are transferred to 2D17-2459 and treated as a motion to review the circuit court order denying appointment of appellate counsel.

The record transmitted by the Hillsborough County Clerk of the Circuit Court for 2D18-311 is transferred to 2D17-2459 and treated as an appendix to the motion to review.

Accordingly, 2D18-311 is dismissed as duplicative of case number 2D17-2459, which remains pending.

NORTHCUTT, KELLY, and LUCAS, JJ., Concur.
